00:10:35.395 --> 00:10:52.058
And you believed and you received it and you just latched on to it, but you're convinced, no matter if you sin or whatever, that you believe that you're saved."I said, "That's right."And he said, "And if they would tell you you weren't saved, you would fight them.

00:10:52.059 --> 00:10:58.178
You would argue with them and say, 'No, I know I'm saved.'They say, 'No, I don't believe you're saved.''No, I know I'm saved.

00:10:58.179 --> 00:11:11.275
You're not going to tell me I'm not saved.'"I said, "That's exactly right,"because I could see myself in this experience saying that as somebody was telling me, "I don't believe you're saved."I said, "Well, I know I'm saved.

00:11:11.276 --> 00:11:14.935
I know I'm saved."And I was fully persuaded that I know I'm saved.

